Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.08,0:01:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:15.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:17.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:21.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\blur1}我便倾诉于你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:30.34,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}啊 虽然这般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:33.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重要的回忆也会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:37.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}被时间之沙掩盖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:41.94,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而变得暧昧不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:48.59,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}说着「命运」这词是如此廉价
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:52.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}而与我一同开怀大笑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:58.44,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}又是否是我生命中的罗密欧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:03.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大家 一定会将自己的珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:06.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}逐渐忘却在心的角落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:10.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}与你的一分一秒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:13.97,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使只有一瞬 也请留在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:17.43,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}即使成为无法集齐的拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.52,0:03:21.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}那无法寻觅的最后一片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}记忆之扉敞开的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}你想一同聆听
